## Headings
- \`<h1>\` to \`<h6>\` - Heading levels (h1 only once per page)

## Text Elements
- \`<p>\` - Paragraph
- \`<strong>\` - Important text
- \`<em>\` - Emphasized text
- \`<br>\` - Line break
- \`<hr>\` - Horizontal line

## Lists
- \`<ul>\` - Unordered list
- \`<ol>\` - Ordered list
- \`<li>\` - List item

## Links and Images
- \`<a href="">\` - Link
- \`<img src="" alt="">\` - Image`
