## HTML5 Input Types
- \`date\` - Date picker
- \`time\` - Time picker
- \`color\` - Color picker
- \`range\` - Slider
- \`file\` - File upload
- \`url\`, \`tel\`, \`search\`

## Form Attributes
- \`required\` - Field required
- \`placeholder\` - Hint text
- \`min/max\` - Value limits
- \`disabled\` - Disable field
- \`readonly\` - Read-only field`
