## Video Tag
\`\`\`html
<video width="320" height="240" controls>
    <source src="movie.mp4" type="video/mp4">
    Your browser does not support video.
</video>
\`\`\`

## Video Attributes
- controls, autoplay, muted
- loop, poster

## Audio Tag
\`\`\`html
<audio controls>
    <source src="audio.mp3" type="audio/mpeg">
</audio>
\`\`\``
