## Canvas - Graphics Container
- Drawn with JavaScript
- Used for games, animations
- Pixel-based (raster)

## SVG - Vector Graphics
- XML-based format
- Perfect for logos, icons
- Scales without quality loss

## Canvas vs SVG
- Canvas: Games, animations
- SVG: Logos, icons, diagrams`
